{"head":{"layout":"RulePage","next":"/user-guide/rules/selector-max-combinators/","prev":"/user-guide/rules/selector-max-attribute/","description":"selector-max-class 限制一个选择器中类的数量 此规则在计算一个选择器的类的数量之前先解析选择器嵌套。选择器列表中的每个选择器都将单独计算。 :not() 伪类的内容也是单独计算的。此规则将其参数视为一个独立的选择器，结果不计入整个选择器的总数。 选项…","title":""},"body":"<h1 id=\"selector-max-class\"><a href=\"#selector-max-class\" class=\"phenomic-HeadingAnchor\">#</a>selector-max-class</h1>\n<p>限制一个选择器中类的数量</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">div</span> <span class=\"hljs-selector-class\">.foo</span><span class=\"hljs-selector-class\">.bar</span><span class=\"hljs-selector-attr\">[data-val]</span> > <span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span><span class=\"hljs-selector-class\">.baz</span> {}\n<span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*  ↑   ↑                 ↑\n    ↑   ↑                 ↑\n    1   2                 3  -- this selector contains three classes */</span></code></pre>\n<p>此规则在计算一个选择器的类的数量之前先解析选择器嵌套。<a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/selectors4/#selector-list\">选择器列表</a>中的每个选择器都将单独计算。</p>\n<p><code>:not()</code> 伪类的内容也是单独计算的。此规则将其参数视为一个独立的选择器，结果不计入整个选择器的总数。</p>\n<h2 id=\"选项\"><a href=\"#%E9%80%89%E9%A1%B9\" class=\"phenomic-HeadingAnchor\">#</a>选项</h2>\n<p><code>int</code>：允许的最大类数量。</p>\n<p>例如，使用 <code>2</code>：</p>\n<p>以下模式被视为违规：</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-class\">.foo</span><span class=\"hljs-selector-class\">.bar</span><span class=\"hljs-selector-class\">.baz</span> {}</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-class\">.foo</span> <span class=\"hljs-selector-class\">.bar</span> {\n  &#x26; > .baz {}\n}</code></pre>\n<p>以下模式<em>不</em>被视为违规：</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">div</span> {}</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-class\">.foo</span> <span class=\"hljs-selector-class\">.bar</span> {}</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-class\">.foo</span><span class=\"hljs-selector-class\">.bar</span>,\n<span class=\"hljs-selector-class\">.lorem</span><span class=\"hljs-selector-class\">.ipsum</span> {} <span class=\"hljs-comment\">/* 选择器列表中的每个选择器都将单独计算 */</span></code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-class\">.foo</span> <span class=\"hljs-selector-class\">.bar</span> <span class=\"hljs-selector-pseudo\">:not(.lorem.ipsum)</span> {} <span class=\"hljs-comment\">/* `.lorem.ipsum` 在 `:not()` 里面，所以它是单独计算的 */</span></code></pre>\n","__filename":"user-guide/rules/selector-max-class.md","__url":"/user-guide/rules/selector-max-class/","__resourceUrl":"/user-guide/rules/selector-max-class/index.html","__dataUrl":"/user-guide/rules/selector-max-class/index.html.4e8a071c2a8f5c531ad10cb68ec05ac7.json"}